FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS

How fast does the product work?

The product starts working within 20 minutes. It calms overactive nerves and relaxes the muscles, quickly reducing urgency and urine leakage. With daily use, you’ll notice lasting improvements.

Is it safe to use?

Absolutely! The product is dermatologically tested and made from high-quality ingredients that are safe for daily use. It has been specially formulated to prevent skin irritation and strengthen the tissue around the bladder.

Can this product completely cure my incontinence?

It significantly helps improve bladder control, reduces leaks, and enhances overall comfort.

How often should I use it?

For optimal results, we recommend applying the product daily, usually once or twice a day, depending on your needs. Consistent use ensures long-term improvements.
